          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2428Step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> ciabatta slices</strong> to one side of a baking tray and drizzle them with<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> walnuts</strong> to the other side and put the tray in the oven for 4-5 min or until everything's lightly toasted</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2428Step-6v2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2428Step-6v2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2428Step-6v2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2428Step-6v2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2428Step-6v2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything's cooking, chop the <strong>apple<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into slices, removing any core</p><p>Add the <strong>baby leaf salad</strong>, <strong>apple slices</strong> and <strong>toasted walnuts </strong>to a bowl with the<strong> balsamic dressing</strong> and gently mix together – this is your<strong> walnut & apple salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2428Step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2428Step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2428Step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2428Step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2428Step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>baked camemberts</strong> topped with the<strong> truffled mushrooms</strong></p><p>Drizzled over any <strong>remaining truffle oil </strong>and serve the<strong> ciabatta slices</strong> and <strong>walnut & apple salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Season with <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
